of water to drink.

06:23.382 --> 06:25.301
♪ Drink, drink,
drink my wee-wee ♪

06:25.384 --> 06:27.136
♪ Oh no ♪

06:27.220 --> 06:29.138
-(singing): I gotta drink it.
-Drink it!

06:29.222 --> 06:31.099
-Drink it!
-Uh, drink it! Oh, fuck!

06:31.182 --> 06:33.017
-Where's Rick? Fuck. We gotta...
-Oh right.

06:33.101 --> 06:35.436
-This is serious.
Pay attention.
-Right. Okay.

06:35.520 --> 06:38.022
(whirring)

06:38.106 --> 06:40.900
-What do you wanna sing
at choir practice tonight?
-Oh, shit.

06:41.818 --> 06:43.778
God, I don't know.

06:43.861 --> 06:46.614
-There's so many
solid gold options.
-Yeah.

06:46.697 --> 06:48.157
Maybe you could
do a rocker.

06:48.241 --> 06:51.285
I don't know. It's only
my second time. It just, uh...

06:51.369 --> 06:52.912
I don't wanna go too crazy.

06:52.995 --> 06:55.623
How about, like,
a little Air Supply?

06:55.706 --> 06:57.083
Or maybe something more classic?

06:57.166 --> 06:59.460
-What's more classic
than Air Supply?
-That's a good point.

06:59.544 --> 07:01.838
-(laughs)
-But are we All Out Of Love,

07:01.921 --> 07:03.506
or are we Lost In Love?

07:03.589 --> 07:05.842
Or are we
Making Love...

07:05.925 --> 07:09.137
Both:
Out Of Nothing At All? (laughs)

07:11.139 --> 07:14.225
♪ ♪

07:30.616 --> 07:33.369
-Tricia: It's cute, right?
-Charity: It's so cute.

07:33.452 --> 07:35.913
-(laughs)
-Tricia: So cute!

07:35.997 --> 07:39.000
(laughs) Come on!

07:39.083 --> 07:42.211
(birds chirping)

07:42.295 --> 07:46.507
-(Beethoven's Fifth ringtone)
-Fuck! (sighs)

07:46.591 --> 07:48.551
-(Sam sighs)
-(Joel laughs)

07:48.634 --> 07:50.344
-Hi, Mom.
-MJ (on phone):
Your father wants to know

07:50.428 --> 07:52.805
if you're coming home
for the barbecue.

07:52.889 --> 07:55.016
I'm making my egg salad...

07:55.099 --> 07:57.560
Oh, you know what? I got
a lot going on today, Mom.

07:57.643 --> 08:01.898
Um, actually,
I-I gotta go. Bye.

08:01.981 --> 08:03.441
