pretty big for me.

08:13.951 --> 08:16.704
-Oh really? You got,
like, a Saturday ritual?
-I do.

08:16.787 --> 08:19.498
-Oh!
-I like to sit down
and write out a list

08:19.582 --> 08:21.751
