a list of accomplishments

08:23.794 --> 08:26.088
-for the previous week
and stuff like that.
-Oh my god!

08:26.172 --> 08:29.383
-That's so amazing!
-Yeah. (laughs)

08:29.467 --> 08:30.760
I don't do any of that.

08:30.843 --> 08:33.179
