drinking wine in my underwear.

08:33.262 --> 08:35.890
-Oh. Hm...
-It's pretty fuckin' great.

08:37.516 --> 08:39.101
Hm.

08:39.185 --> 08:41.187
"Hm" what?

08:41.270 --> 08:42.772
I don't know.

08:43.689 --> 08:46.400
Just... sounds a little lonely.

08:48.736 --> 08:51.405
Yeah, well,
it works for me.

08:51.489 --> 08:53.491
Okay.

08:53.574 --> 08:55.785
And what do you do
with your Saturdays?

08:57.536 --> 09:00.373
