stuff mostly.

09:00.456 --> 09:04.168
I do ESL, I do
youth group mentoring.

09:04.252 --> 09:06.462
Today, we're packing up, uh,

09:06.545 --> 09:09.423
donations from the canned
good and toiletry drive.

09:09.507 --> 09:11.634
Then, I'm gonna set up
for choir practice.

09:11.717 --> 09:14.303
Every other weekend,
I have this volunteer gig

09:14.387 --> 09:16.389
at the pediatric clinic.

09:16.472 --> 09:19.141
And then, I do
sometimes do clowning

09:19.225 --> 09:22.395
-for the kids in the hospital.
-(laughs) Jesus.

09:22.478 --> 09:25.523
You do so much stuff.

09:25.606 --> 09:27.900
Eh. I just...

09:27.984 --> 09:29.402
try to keep busy,

09:29.485 --> 09:33.322
-make sure that the terror
doesn't creep in.
-(both laugh)

09:33.406 --> 09:36.117
(gasps)
Rick is on the move.
He's on the move!

09:36.200 --> 09:37.576
-Well, fuck, let's go!
-Oh.

09:37.660 --> 09:40.162
-Okay. Um...
-(starts car)

09:41.455 --> 09:43.207
