then hang back.

09:51.299 --> 09:53.259
-Joel...
-Oh wait, I'm just
gonna let this guy go.

09:53.342 --> 09:55.636
Sam:
Joel, no, no, no! Go around,
or we're gonna lose him!

09:55.720 --> 09:57.221
Joel: Well, no.
I can't go around.

09:57.305 --> 09:58.848
-Joel--
-What about oncoming traffic?

09:58.931 --> 10:01.600
You just said that there were
no other cars, Joel! Hit it!

10:01.684 --> 10:04.270
-No... No. It's too risky!
-No, no, no! Hit it! Go!

10:04.353 --> 10:05.813
