You can't hesitate!

10:05.896 --> 10:06.814
Just pull up and go around.

10:06.897 --> 10:08.566
-You can do it!
-Don't hesitate.

10:08.649 --> 10:10.776
Both:
Don't hesitate.
Don't hesitate.

10:10.860 --> 10:11.861
Hit it!

10:11.944 --> 10:13.863
-(engine revving)
-Joel: Oh... no!

10:13.946 --> 10:15.906
-I'm sorry, I hesitated.
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
-Joel!

10:15.990 --> 10:17.616
Joel, we're gonna lose him!
Go! Go! Go!

10:17.700 --> 10:20.077
-Don't hesitate! Just go!
-Joel: Oh god! Ah!

10:20.161 --> 10:21.996
-Ah! Car! There's a car!
-Ah! Go! Go! Go!

10:22.079 --> 10:23.414
-(honking)
-(screaming)

10:23.497 --> 10:26.334
-Oh god! (laughing)
-You did it!
You did it! You did it!

10:26.417 --> 10:29.378
-You did it! (laughs)
-Oh, that was scary and fun!

10:29.462 --> 10:31.547
-(laughs)
-Sam: Oh no!

10:31.630 --> 10:34.967
-Oh no, no, no, where's Rick?
-God, where is he?

10:35.051 --> 10:38.304
-Fuck, we lost him. Fuck...
-(ringtone)

10:39.180 --> 10:41.015
(sighs)

10:41.098 --> 10:42.516
-Hi, honey.
-Michael (on phone):
Where are you?

10:42.600 --> 10:44.143
-I thought we were
getting lunch.
-Oh, I'm sorry.

10:44.226 --> 10:46.228
I'm just helping Sam
out with something.

10:46.312 --> 10:47.563
Michael:
What does she need help with?

10:47.646 --> 10:49.482
Just some music
and stuff for tonight.

10:49.565 --> 10:52.360
-Michael: Okay. Joel?
Have fun with Sam.
-Wha--

10:54.570 --> 10:56.739
-Michael says hi.
-Sam: Really?

10:56.822 --> 10:58.949
(tractor rumbling)

11:01.452 --> 11:04.580
(trailer rattling)

11:07.750 --> 11:08.709
(sighs)

11:08.793 --> 11:11.754
♪ ♪

11:11.837 --> 11:14.965
(birds chirping)

11:33.651 --> 11:35.444
Ed:
Ah. What is this, a leap year?

11:35.528 --> 11:37.697
How did we get
to be so lucky?

11:37.780 --> 11:39.407
