of you forever.

14:51.932 --> 14:56.270
(country music
playing on stereo)

14:56.353 --> 14:58.355
Wouldn't you be more
comfortable at the table?

14:58.439 --> 15:00.149
Eh, too comfortable
where I am.

15:00.232 --> 15:02.484
