I know you can bring it.

17:28.297 --> 17:31.759
-I'm excited. Alright?
Let 'er rip! Let 'er rip!
-Alright, let it rip.

17:31.842 --> 17:33.886
(harp playing stops)

17:33.969 --> 17:37.473
